dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, buildings, people, roads and paths.

Features 6 pictorial vignettes: Joodse Hoogpriester in zyn hoog priesterlyk gewaad -- Koperen wasvat -- Gouden tafel der toonbrooden -- Gouden reukautaar -- Gouden kandelaar -- Joods priester op den verzoendag.
